&lt;/h2&gt;</description></item><item><title>Scissor &amp; Viewport</title><link>//pmndrs.github.io/postprocessing/manual/demos/utility/scissor-viewport/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>vanruesc@outlook.de (Raoul van Rüschen)</author><guid>//pmndrs.github.io/postprocessing/manual/demos/utility/scissor-viewport/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="scissor--viewport"&gt;
	&lt;span&gt;Scissor &amp;amp; Viewport&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="//pmndrs.github.io/postprocessing/manual/demos/utility/scissor-viewport/#scissor--viewport" data-pagefind-ignore&gt;¶&lt;/a&gt;
